column5: My wife and I went to Kenora today for bit of shopping and give my arm some more rest from pounding some huge walleyes on Lac Suel again from Onaway Lodge.Also decided t√≤ go take a look first hand of Huskie the Muskie new paint job.I can live with it but really don't like.Color just isn't right and it looks more like a tiger muskie than a barred muskie.Iam sure some of you have seen the original Huskie the Muskie.Lets here some feedback.my wife in picture from last summer and me with new pic.
